'''羅德·席爾瓦'''（{{lang-en|Rod Silva}}；{{bd|1972年||}}），是美國一名[[餐饮家|餐饮家]]，他代表營養黨參選[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]<ref name="fec">{{cite web |last1=Silva |first1=Rod |title=FEC Form 2: Statement of Candidacy |url=http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/407/201510209003140407/201510209003140407.pdf |website=[[Federal_Election_Commission|fec.gov]] |accessdate=2015-12-22 |date=2015-10-20 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427072353/http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/407/201510209003140407/201510209003140407.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="silva2016">{{cite web |last1=Silva |first1=Rod |title=My fellow Americans |url=http://rodsilva2016.com/ |website=Rod Silva for President 2016 |accessdate=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223171640/http://rodsilva2016.com/ |archive-date=2015-12-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==背景==
席爾瓦在[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[紐華克_(新澤西州)|紐華克]]出生，是一位巴西移民的兒子<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ferreira |first1=Leonardo |title=Filho de brasileiros em New Jersey é candidato a presidente dos EUA |url=http://www.brazilianvoice.com/bv_noticias/filho-de-brasileiros-em-new-jersey-e-candidato-a-presidente-dos-eua.html |website=Brazilian Voice |accessdate=2015-12-23 |language=pt |date=2015-11-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226194224/http://www.brazilianvoice.com/bv_noticias/filho-de-brasileiros-em-new-jersey-e-candidato-a-presidente-dos-eua.html |archivedate=2015年12月26日 |df= }}</ref>。他在1995年創立肌肉製作燒烤（{{lang|en|Muscle Maker Grill}}）餐廳，旨在提供健康的[[快餐|快餐]]替代品<ref>{{cite news |last1=Reysen |first1=Jamie |title=Muscle Maker Grill founder Rod Silva enters presidential race, pledges to 'make America healthy again' |url=http://www.amny.com/news/muscle-maker-grill-founder-rod-silva-enters-presidential-race-pledges-to-make-america-healthy-again-1.11053722 |accessdate=2015-12-23 |work=[[AM_New_York|AM New York]] |date=2015-11-03 |archive-date=2019-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004012609/https://www.amny.com/news/muscle-maker-grill-founder-rod-silva-enters-presidential-race-pledges-to-make-america-healthy-again-1.11053722 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這一間[[快速休閒餐廳|快速休閒餐廳]]2007年成為[[加盟連鎖|加盟連鎖]]品牌<ref>{{cite web |last1=Crouch |first1=Sudie |title=Muscle Maker Grill Promotes Morgan To President And CEO |url=http://www.shelbyfoodservice.com/2015/10/23/muscle-maker-grill-promotes-morgan-to-president-and-ceo/ |website=Shelby Food Service |accessdate=2015-12-23 |date=2015-10-23 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

==競逐美國總統==
新泽西州[[皮斯卡特维_(新泽西州)|皮斯卡特维]]居民席爾瓦於2015年10月20日提交了美國總統候選人資格聲明書<ref name="fec"/> 。根據他的競選網站，他的平台「將重點關注首先解決在美國國內發生的嚴重問題，例如增加的肥胖率、糖尿病、高血壓、膽固醇和其他健康相關的併發症——所有這些都是由於飲食選擇不當造成的」<ref name="silva2016"/>。

他只在科羅拉多州列入選票。截至2016年10月，在科羅拉多州的選票中他的副總統競選拍檔為理查德·席爾瓦（{{lang|en|Richard Silva}}）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Winger |first1=Richard |authorlink1=Richard Winger |title=Nutrition Party Announces Presidential Candidate, and Qualifies Him for Colorado Ballot |url=http://ballot-access.org/2015/12/22/nutrition-party-announces-presidential-candidates-and-qualifies-him-for-colorado-ballot/ |website=[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]] |accessdate=2015-12-22 |date=2015-12-22 |archive-date=2015-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223144544/http://ballot-access.org/2015/12/22/nutrition-party-announces-presidential-candidates-and-qualifies-him-for-colorado-ballot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

